1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,500
FanQuest Agent turns every World Cup match
into a guided fan journey.

2
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:11,000
Fans create an identity and connect an Injective testnet wallet,
with a clear review fallback.

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:17,000
They pick a live match, join a quest, and lock winner,
scoring team, and player predictions.

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:22,500
The result resolves in seconds,
calculating points from match data.

5
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:28,000
An open-box reveal transforms the outcome
into an emotional reward moment.

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:34,000
Points update the leaderboard,
then the fan creates an on-chain claim receipt.

7
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:40,000
The wallet view separates confirmed proof
from demo reward accounting.

8
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,500
A share-ready X post closes the loop:
predict, compete, reveal, rank, and share.

9
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:52,500
The Injective EVM testnet transaction
is publicly verifiable in Blockscout.

10
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:59,500
Status, block, gas, and the FanQuest claim memo
make the journey provable end to end.
